title: Casebook of Sherlock Holmes
description:
12 x 45 mins (2 series, each of 6 eps)

Once again, Holmes and Watson - Clive Merrison and the late Michael Williams aka. Mr Judi Dench - are on the trail of criminals. The stories in this set are:

Series 1

1: The Adventure of the Illustrious Client
2: The Adventure of the Blanched Soldier
3: The Adventure of the Mazarin Stone
4: The Adventure of the Three Gables
5: The Adventure of the Sussex Vampire
6: The Adventure of the Three Garridebs

Series 2

1: The Problem of Thor Bridge
2: The Adventure of the Creeping Man
3: The Adventure of the Lion's Mane
4: The Adventure of the Veiled Lodger
5: The Adventure of Shoscombe Old Place
6: The Adventure of the Retired Colourman
